#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_call_to_action
msgid "<b>50,000 people</b>, run Clean to grow their financial wealth."
msgstr ""
"<b>50.000 mennesker</b> bruger Clean til at øge deres økonomiske formue."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_cover
msgid "<b>Sell from your couch</b>"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_title
msgid "<b>We create the perfect <br/>tailored solution for you</b>"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_carousel
msgid ""
"<br/>At any moment, you may contact our advisor through the in-app video "
"meeting system."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_carousel
msgid ""
"<br/>We integrate digital tools and solutions for better insights, enabling "
"data-driven planning."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_carousel
msgid ""
"<br/>We invest in strategic advice tailored to your<br/>\n"
"                            business problems and needs."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_features
msgid "All in one"
msgstr "Alt i ét"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Composed of 25 people from 25 to 66 years, we’re a young and dynamic "
"company. We have open positions, do not hesitate to contact us."
msgstr ""
"Vi er en ung og dynamisk virksomhed med 25 medarbejdere i alderen 25 til 66 "
"år. Vi har ledige stillinger, så tøv ikke med at kontakte os."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_features
msgid "Easy to use"
msgstr "Nem at bruge"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_carousel
msgid "Efficient team processes"
msgstr "Effektive teamprocesser"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_text_image
msgid "Everything you need, <br/>totally free"
msgstr "Alt, hvad du har brug for, <br/>helt gratis"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_call_to_action
msgid "Join them and make the right money move."
msgstr "Bliv en del af dem, og tag det rigtige økonomiske skridt."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_cover
msgid ""
"Make your finances reach a new level with our online management system. "
"<br/>Track every penny, directly from the comfort of your home."
msgstr ""
"Løft din økonomi til et nyt niveau med vores online administrationssystem, "
"<br/>og få fuldt overblik over hver eneste krone – direkte og bekvemt "
"hjemmefra."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_three_columns
msgid "Our mission"
msgstr "Vores mission"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_three_columns
msgid "Our team"
msgstr "Vores team"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_three_columns
msgid "Our values"
msgstr "Vores værdier"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_carousel
msgid "Personal adviser"
msgstr "Personlig rådgiver"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Provide clear and concise financial advices to make your financial wealth "
"grow. And this, completely free of charge."
msgstr ""
"Få klare og præcise økonomiske råd, så din formue vokser. Og det helt gratis."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_features
msgid "Secured"
msgstr "Låst"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_carousel
msgid "Simplify things"
msgstr "Gør det enkelt"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_clean.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Designværktøjer"

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_text_image
msgid ""
"Track every expenses, uncover new ways to save, choose the right credit "
"cards. <br/>All those advices and much more are included and totally free of"
" charge."
msgstr ""
"Hold styr på dine udgifter, find nye måder at spare penge på, og vælg de "
"rigtige kreditkort. <br/>Alle disse råd og meget mere er inkluderet – helt "
"gratis."

#. module: theme_clean
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_clean.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"We created our company to improve the work-life balance. We believe that we "
"need to focus on our family more than our work and finances."
msgstr ""
"Vi har grundlagt vores virksomhed for at skabe en bedre balance mellem "
"arbejde og privatliv. Vi mener, at familien bør komme før arbejde og økonomi."

